localized-strings.tagline: A Framework for Integrating Linguistic Analysis and Semantic Annotation of Text Documents.

pages-strings.A Framework for Integrating Linguistic A: A Framework for Integrating Linguistic Analysis and Semantic Annotation of Text Documents.
pages-strings.DeepNLPF provides a component for integr: DeepNLPF provides a component for integrating and customizing linguistic analysis. When building Plugins, you can add any PLN tool, regardless of the programming language in which it was created.
pages-strings.DeepNLPF includes parallel processing st: DeepNLPF includes parallel processing strategies and multithreads to ensure maximum performance. Through the approach taken it is possible to process extremely large texts.
pages-strings.DeepNLPF has two approaches to optimize: DeepNLPF has two approaches to optimize execution. By default we use [Multiprocessing Pathos Framework](https://pypi.org/project/pathos/), but if you prefer you can choose to use [Faster Parallel Ray](https://ray.io/) 10x [fast as the first one](https://towardsdatascience.com/10x-faster-parallel-python-without-python-multiprocessing-e5017c93cce1).
pages-strings.DeepNLPF contains a DashBoard that allow: DeepNLPF contains a DashBoard that allows you to view and process textual data without writing any lines of code and with few settings, choosing from various linguistic analyzes coming from a number of successful PLN tools.
pages-strings.DeepNLPF has a flexible plugin architect: DeepNLPF has a flexible plugin architecture, allowing the integration of various third party PLN tools, regardless of the programming language in which it was built, it can be integrated into the analysis pipeline.
pages-strings.DeepNLPF has a very simple solution for: DeepNLPF has a very simple solution for you to use natural language processing in your web, mobile or desktop application reducing the computational cost. Using the API we have provided you make this hard work for us and consume only the results of the analysis that interests you.
pages-strings.You don't have to spend hours shipping t: You don't have to spend hours shipping the computer waiting for your dataset to finish processing. BotNotification is responsible for keeping you informed about everything that happens during processing, you are the one who chooses the best way that it can do this, either through (Telegram, Email, Desktop Notifications or even by voice). What's up! liked? Take your time to relax, let BotNotification take care of everything for you.
pages-strings.Install plugins and pipeline with our co: Install plugins and pipeline with our command line interface.
pages-strings.Here you will find all external tool plu: Here you will find all external tool plugins built by us and third parties to use on DeepNLPF.
pages-strings.Did not find what you were looking for?: Did not find what you were looking for? Create your plugin now and help DeeoNLPF grow.
pages-strings.Choose from the best natural language pr: Choose from the best natural language processing tools and add them to your analysis pipeline.
pages-strings.Use semantic dictionaries in your pipeli: Use semantic dictionaries in your pipeline and better results.
pages-strings.Save and explore your datasets through a: Save and explore your datasets through a database.
pages-strings.This project is maintained by a dedicate: This project is maintained by a dedicated group of people.
